<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="EI=egde">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
	<link rel="stylesheet"  href="../style.css" >
	<link rel="stylesheet"  href="../bootstrap/css/bootstrap.css" >
    <style>
        #details article img {
            height :300px;
        }
    </style>
	<title><%= title %></title>
</head>
<body>
<main>


<section class="container-fluid" id="details">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <article class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                <aside class="flexy-col">
                    <h2>Personal Infomation</h2>
                    <div class="">
                        <img src="<%=driver[0].imgper%>" alt="" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="">
                        <h5>TRAVELS</h5>
                        <p>FROM : <%=driver[0].location%></p>
                        <p>To :  <%=driver[0].destination%></p>
                        <p>Depart Time :  <%=driver[0].leavingtime%></p>
                        <p>Car : BMW , 2018 , red Voilet</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="">
                        <p>Name :<%=driver[0].name%></p>
                        <p>Current Location : <%=driver[0].location%></p></p>
                        <p>Destination :<%=driver[0].destination%></p></p>
                        <p>Cellphone : 076 176 2729</p>
                        <p>WhatsApp : 076 176 27 29</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="">
                        <h5>ABOUT</h5>
                        <p>My strength is utilizing Javascript, whether React or backend Node applications. With it, I have developed applications that are engaging in user experience which my clients cannot stop sharing. I pride myself on the love of challenge. What I am looking for is to join a team to which I can add a value.</p>
                    </div>
                </aside>
            </article>
            <article class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
                <aside class="flexy-col">
                    <h2>Vehicle Details</h2>
                    <div class="details-img">
                        <img src="<%=driver[0].imgcar%>" alt="" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="">
                        <p>Make :<%=driver[0].car%></p></p>
                        <p>Model : 2018</p>
                        <p>Colour : red</p>
                        <p>Total Seats: 4 </p>
                    </div>
                </aside>
            </article>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


</main>
</body>
</html>